message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM. The paper deals with deep neural networks for image classification, specifically for fine-grained datasets. This falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of spatial grounding and reasoning, which is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the paper deals with image datasets, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM).
